OL,3,CRenewed appeal over murder of man
OL,4,Cfound dead in Armagh 40 years ago
OL,6,FA renewed appeal for information has
OL,7,Fbeen issued about the murder of a man
OL,8,Ffound in County Armagh 40 years ago.
OL,10,FThe remains of Terence "Terry"
OL,11,FMcKeever, 30, were found close to
OL,12,FMullaghduff Bridge, Cullyhanna on June
OL,13,F16, 1986.
OL,15,FMr McKeever, originally from Armagh
OL,16,Fbut living in Dublin, was the managing
OL,17,Fdirector of a family electrical
OL,18,Fcontracting business based both north
OL,19,Fand south of the border.
OL,26,@rD@XOUrD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
