OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781621295
OL,3,CRenewed appeal over murder of man
OL,4,Cfound dead in Armagh 40 years ago
OL,6,FThe electrical company was involved in
OL,7,Flarge contract works north and south
OL,8,Fof the border, which included army
OL,9,Fbarracks, Garda and RUC stations.
OL,10,FGardai believe that he was abducted
OL,11,Fand fatally shot.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, Gardai appealed to anyone
OL,14,Fwith any information they feel might
OL,15,Fbe relevant to the investigation to
OL,16,Fget in contact.
OL,18,FMr McKeever left his home at Pembroke
OL,19,FRoad, Ballsbridge in a champagne-
OL,20,Fcoloured BMW 735i with the
OL,21,Fregistration FIB 735.
OL,26,@rD@FrtuD@Rrt
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
