OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781621295
OL,3,CRenewed appeal over murder of man
OL,4,Cfound dead in Armagh 40 years ago
OL,6,FHe left at on 6.50am on June 16 1986
OL,7,Fand is believed to have travelled
OL,8,Fnorth along the N2 from Dublin.
OL,10,FIt is believed that he was abducted in
OL,11,Fthe vicinity of the Monaghan/south
OL,12,FArmagh border area, or somewhere
OL,13,Fduring his intended route which would
OL,14,Fhave included the N2 from Dublin,
OL,15,Fpassing through Slane, Ardee, Monaghan
OL,16,Fand continuing to Armagh town.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
