PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781621295
OL,3,CRenewed appeal over murder of man
OL,4,Cfound dead in Armagh 40 years ago
OL,6,FHis remains were found near
OL,7,FMullaghduff Bridge, around 25 metres
OL,8,Finto Northern Ireland, on that day and
OL,9,Fthe following day, June 17, his car
OL,10,Fwas found in Carnagh, County Armagh.
OL,12,FOn June 18 1986, a blue Toyota Liteace
OL,13,Fvan with stolen number plates UZY 125
OL,14,Fwas found abandoned on the N52 at
OL,15,FMapastown, Ardee, County Louth.
OL,17,FGardai said it is believed to have
OL,18,Fbeen the vehicle used in the murder of
OL,19,FMr McKeever.
OL,26,@yD@Frt
