OL,3,CRenewed appeal over murder of man
OL,4,Cfound dead in Armagh 40 years ago
OL,6,FThe van had been stolen in Dundalk on
OL,7,FMay 21 1986.
OL,9,FGardai area asking people if they have
OL,10,Finformation about the van or the
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,F"Do you have any information that may
OL,14,Fassist with the investigation?
OL,26,@qD@FrtuD@AOU
