OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781621295
OL,3,CRenewed appeal over murder of man
OL,4,Cfound dead in Armagh 40 years ago
OL,6,F"With the passage of time, some person
OL,7,Fmay now be in a position to provide
OL,8,Finformation to investigating Gardai
OL,9,Fthat they could not provide at the
OL,10,Ftime, or maybe some person who did
OL,11,Fprovide information at the time may be
OL,12,Fnow in a position to provide further
OL,13,Finformation.
OL,15,F"Gardai encourage anyone who they may
OL,16,For may not have spoken to previously,
OL,17,Fto come forward.
OL,19,F"Investigating Gardai are particularly
OL,20,Finterested in information on the
OL,21,Ffollowing:
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@crtwD@AOUwD@Grt{D@AOU{D@Urt
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
