OL,3,CRenewed appeal over murder of man
OL,4,Cfound dead in Armagh 40 years ago
OL,6,F"Terence McKeever's movements on the
OL,7,Fmorning of 16th June 1986
OL,9,F"The theft and storage of a blue
OL,10,FToyota LiteAce van registration number
OL,11,F7533 KI (or the stolen registration
OL,12,Fnumber UZY 125 between 21st May 1986
OL,13,Fand 18th June 1986.
OL,15,F"The movements of Mr McKeever's
OL,16,Fchampagne-coloured BMW 735i
OL,17,F(registration FIB 735, which was
OL,18,Fsubsequently found at Carnagh, Co
OL,19,FArmagh on 17th June 1986).
